description:
This is a 12 minute workout called 'Start your day with this!' from the channel Breathe and Flow.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is a short ten minute all purpose all levels natural and functional movement and yoga routine to start your day right! Do this every morning, evening, after any other workout of just in between.
